data.description: Cute ranch on a corner lot in the heart of Fuquay-Varina, close to all shops and amenities, is the perfect starter home!  Just imagine what you can do with this property, the potential is great!  With little TLC this can be the affordable house you've been looking for.  This house boasts of an open kitchen/dining area with plenty of counterspace and cabinets, even though is a small house, it has plenty of storage. Please check schools designations if important to you.  Come make this house your own!  .GREAT LOCATION! Some photos are digitally staged.
